# Optional. The app works fine anonymously (TfL allows ~50 requests/min without
# a key, and this app caches aggressively), but if you hit rate limits you can
# register a free account at https://api-portal.tfl.gov.uk and paste your key
# here to raise the limit to 500 requests/min.
#
# On Vercel: set this as an Environment Variable in the project settings.
TFL_APP_KEY=
